Value.value: As soon as you descend the stairs, a magical barrier phases into existence behind you, trapping you inside.

value.0:
This device has no apparent hallmark, but it appears to be some form of magical siphon or barrier. It is quite powerful, but looks like it could be on the verge of instability. Perhaps some additional magic source might tip it over the edge...

// Activated by using Greater Mythal on it. Once enough have been used, it will activate the boss fight. Only one mythal may be used per character. Be warned: This is dangerous!
